paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the upregulation of transthyretin (TTR) in a porcine model of branch retinal vein occlusion (BRVO) following bevacizumab treatment. No specific genetic variants in the TTR gene were reported.

challenges: The paper did not report any specific genetic variants in the TTR gene.
extraction_metadata.notes: The focus of the paper was on protein expression changes rather than genetic variants.
